_sText:
Second map I deem worthy of release, didn't spend much time on this one, but it plays well, is 100% even, has some nice light, and is highly optimized(260-160 FPS), was made with a underground arena in mind, sort of like a private underground club, remade especially for CSS. Think fight club.

This is my first attempt at a aim map, so give me some tips on improving all you aim players!

Can support 64 players, made by CaiD/Cook me DinnaH!

Give me tips on what to add to this map, and feedback too please.

Thanks.
